    "Otherwise, if the seed is deemed uninteresting, PlateauLen is incremented by 1 (line 32).Based on the value of PlateauLen, we determine whether the fuzzer has entered the coverage plateau.",
    "If PlateauLen does not exceed MaxPlateau, the predefined maximum length of the coverage plateau (line 11), our LLMPF mutates messages using the strategy introduced earlier.",
    "The value of MaxPlateau is specified by users and provided to the fuzzer.",
    "However, when PlateauLen surpasses MaxPlateau, we consider the fuzzer to have entered the coverage plateau.",
    "In such case, LLMPF will utilize the LLM to overcome the coverage plateau (lines [19][20][21]."
  ],
